@startuml fig-ci-github-actions
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
left to right direction

title GitHub Actions — E2 Smoke and PCAP Workflow

card "Trigger\npush / pull_request" as trigger #FFE0B2

package "Job: e2 (ubuntu-latest)" as job #F5F5F5 {

  card "Step 1\nCheckout\n(actions/checkout@v4)" as checkout #E3F2FD

  card "Step 2\nBuild and Run E2\ndocker compose up\n--build\n--exit-code-from tester" as build #BBDEFB

  card "Step 3\nUpload Artefacts\n(actions/upload-artifact@v4)\npath: artifacts/" as upload #C8E6C9
}

card "Result\nPASS / FAIL" as result #FFF9C4

trigger --> checkout : on event
checkout --> build : repository ready
build --> upload : always\n(if: always())
upload --> result : artefacts archived

note right of build
  docker compose starts all services
  and the tester container.
  The tester exit code determines
  the job outcome.
end note

legend bottom
The workflow runs on every push and pull request.
Step 3 uploads artifacts/ regardless of outcome
so that PCAP files are available for debugging.
The --exit-code-from flag propagates tester status.
endlegend
@enduml
